metaDescription: The masterclass offers an in-depth exploration of Tabla solo performance. This is an opportunity to participate in an intensive workshop for talented young Tabla students by the world renowned Tabla player Yogesh Samsi, disciple of the late Ustad Allarakha and will be held on Saturday 26th July & Sunday 27th July 2025 via Zoom (Video conferencing & Webinar Platform).
title: November 2025
